                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">City police-constable, No</hi>, 315.) I produce a certificate from Mr. Clark's office, of both the prisoners' former conviction—(<hi rend="italic">read</hi>)—I was present at the trial, and I know them to be the persons.</p>
